com.indeed.status.core

Class CheckResult

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.indeed.status.core.CheckResult

  • public class CheckResult
extends Object
    The CheckResult represents the outcome of a single dependency check. This object is immutable and may be persisted indefinitely to communicate the snapshot status of the dependency to interested parties.
